{"tid":494375,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲總理譚保講普通話表明不向中國屈服","createTime":"2017-12-09T14:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T17:42:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a1eaaf80c2191acfcc7e90566c7161d5250289bf","tid":494375,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:25:28.000Z","msg":"譚保稱，中國在 1949 年建國時，毛澤東在天安門城樓上宣布「中國人民站起來了」，是中國人對主權的宣示和自信。 <br />\n<br />\n他用普通話稱「澳大利亞人民站起來」，強調澳洲人有同樣的主權和自信，他重申，絕不允許中國干預澳洲內政。 <br />\n<br />\n這相信是澳中建交以來，澳洲總理就中國問題發表過的講話中最強硬的。 <br />\n<br />\n澳洲即使在 1990 時代台灣海峽危機和 2000 年代力拓間諜風波期間，總理都未曾發表過這樣的「狠話」。 <br />\n<br />\n譚保表示，自己在中國有數十年的營商經驗，不認為像參議員達斯艾利那樣，為「幾千元的好處」向中國屈服會得到中國人的尊重。 <br />\n<br />\n譚保正積極立例防止外國政治捐獻和干預澳洲內政。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/yourlanguage/cantonese/zh-hant/article/2017/12/09/tan-bao-jiang-pu-tong-hua-biao-ming-bu-xiang-zhong-guo-qu-fu-you-pian?language=zh-hant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Fyourlanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Farticle%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2Ftan-bao-jiang-pu-tong-hua-biao-ming-bu-xiang-zhong-guo-qu-fu-you-pian%3Flanguage%3Dzh-hant&d=I9q57khBnM14iE4uKaveFpUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=4687a341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/yourlanguage/cantonese/zh-hant/article/2017/12/09/tan-bao-jiang-pu-tong-hua-biao-ming-bu-xiang-zhong-guo-qu-fu-you-pian?language=zh-hant</a>"},{"pid":"1edd71577d4c4e74030dbe37598099f2c8a48048","tid":494375,"uid":77134,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:28:05.000Z","msg":"用普通話咪屈服左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 口裏說不"},{"pid":"0a5dc4327ad614268ea609f8be0ad19daa9f26ba","tid":494375,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:29:20.000Z","msg":"澳洲人？算吧啦"},{"pid":"24fdfdf6e1ab9f2d0afa9e53e980e39bdaa2aeef","tid":494375,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>